---
title: Thai-Style Chicken 'Pad Krapow' with Green Beans
description: Pad krapow is a popular dish in the Thai street food scene. In our version, ground chicken is stir-fried with aromatic ingredients such as ginger, garlic, lime and chili pepper, then served over fluffy rice.
